725976f-a.title: Queens: 169th Street - 89th Avenue
725976f-a.text:
168th Street, west side, south from 89th to 90th
Avenues, showing old damaica homes. On the left is
St. Stephens Protestant Episcopal Church. 168th Street,
here, was previously known as Grand Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  April 6, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
